Pseudomicrothecium Y. 
<normalizedToken id="CCC6D20C398FAF2F0299F89ACD5B8343" originalValue="Marín">Marin</normalizedToken>
, Stchigel, Guarro, Cano, gen. nov.
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
